      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "matthew",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "Matthew 2:3",
      "text": "ܫܡܥ ܕܝܢ ܗܪܘܕܤ ܡܠܟܐ ܘܐܬܬܙܝܥ ܘܟܠܗ ܐܘܪܫܠܡ ܥܡܗ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
