      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "matthew",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "Matthew 2:5",
      "text": "ܗܢܘܢ ܕܝܢ ܐܡܪܘ ܒܒܝܬ ܠܚܡ ܕܝܗܘܕܐ ܗܟܢܐ ܓܝܪ ܟܬܝܒ ܒܢܒܝܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
